<lb n="0494a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0494a2301">如是誦大明加持已出於城外。以<note n="0494a2301" resp="CBETA" type="add">戌【CB】【麗-CB】，戍【大】</note><app n="0494a2301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">戌<note type="cf1">K34n1216_p0416a16</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">戍</rdg></app>時面向
